<div class="yousay">
  Hi, Iâ€™m calling to ask about getting the COVID vaccine for a person over 65.
  Could I please speak to the pharmacist on duty?
</div>

<div class="instructions">Once you reach the right person, ask</div>
<div class="yousay">
  Are you currently offering COVID-19 vaccines to members of the public?
</div>
<form id="callScriptForm">
  <div id="noOptions" class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      id="noNever"
      data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      value="No: will never be a vaccination site"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noNever"> Never </label>

    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      id="noPrivate"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      value="No: not open to the public"
      data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noPrivate">
      Private facility
    </label>
    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript"
      id="noStaffOnly"
      value="No: only vaccinating staff"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noStaffOnly"> Only staff </label>

    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript"
      id="noHCWOnly"
      value="No: only vaccinating health care workers"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noHCWOnly">
      Only health care workers
    </label>
  </div>

  <div id="yesOptions" class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input
      type="radio"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      value="Yes"
      id="yesJustYes"
      class="btn-check"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-success" for="yesJustYes"> Yes we are </label>
    <input
      type="radio"
      id="yesSoon"
      value="Yes: coming soon"
      class="btn-check"
      name="yesNoSelect"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-success" for="yesSoon">
      We will be soon
    </label>
  </div>

  <div id="vaccinatingPublicScript">
    <div class="yousay">How old do seniors need to be to get vaccinated?</div>
    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 65+"
        id="over65"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="over65"> 65 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 70+"
        id="over70"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="over70"> 70 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 75+"
        id="over75"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="over75"> 75 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 80+"
        id="over80"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="over80"> 80 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 85+"
        id="over85"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="over85"> 85 </label>
    </div>
    <div class="yousay">Thanks! Do they need an appointment?</div>

    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointment"
        value="Yes: walk-ins accepted"
        id="apptWalkin"
        data-hide-on-select="appointmentDetails"
        href="#appointmentInfo"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="apptWalkin">
        Walkins are welcome</label
      >
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointment"
        value="Yes: appointment required"
        id="apptReqd"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="apptReqd">
        Appointment Required</label
      >
    </div>
    <div id="appointmentDetails">
      <div class="yousay">
        Do you know if you have any appointments available in the next two
        weeks?
      </div>
      <input type="checkbox" name="appointmentsFull" id="apptFull" />
      <label class="" for="apptsFull"
        >The schedule is full for the next two weeks</label
      >
      <div class="yousay">How should they make the appointment?</div>
      <div class="btn-group" role="group">
        <input
          class="btn-check"
          type="radio"
          name="appointmentMethod"
          id="appointmentMethodCounty"
          value="county"
        /><label for="appointmentMethodCounty" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
          >County website</label
        >
        <input
          class="btn-check"
          type="radio"
          name="appointmentMethod"
          id="appointmentMethodMyTurn"
          value="myturn"
        /><label for="appointmentMethodMyTurn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
          >myturn.ca.gov</label
        >
        <input
          type="radio"
          class="btn-check"
          name="appointmentMethod"
          id="appointmentMethodPhone"
          data-show-also="appointmentPhone"
          value="phone"
        /><label for="appointmentMethodPhone" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
          >phone</label
        >
        <input
          class="btn-check"
          type="radio"
          name="appointmentMethod"
          id="appointmentMethodWeb"
          data-show-also="appointmentWebsite"
          value="web"
        /><label for="appointmentMethodWeb" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
          >web</label
        >
        <input
          class="btn-check"
          type="radio"
          name="appointmentMethod"
          id="appointmentMethodOther"
          data-show-also="appointmentOtherInstructions"
          value="other"
        /><label for="appointmentMethodOther" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
          >Another way</label
        >
      </div>
      <div id="appointmentMethodDetail">
        <input
          type="text"
          id="appointmentPhone"
          class="form-control hidden"
          placeholder="Appointment phone number"
          value="{{locationPhone}}"
        />
        <input
          type="text"
          id="appointmentOtherInstructions"
          class="form-control hidden"
          placeholder="Scheduling instructions"
        />
        <input
          type="text"
          id="appointmentWebsite"
          class="form-control hidden"
          placeholder="Appointment website"
          value="{{locationWebsite}}"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="expansions">
      <div class="yousay">
        Are there any other groups you are able to offer vaccines to?
      </div>
        <input
          class="btn-check"
          type="checkbox"
          id="essentialWorkersAccepted"
        /><label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="essentialWorkersAccepted"
          >Essential workers</label
        >

        <div class="instructions small secondary">
          If they say anything that's not on the list, mention it in the public
          notes.
        </div>
        <div class="restrictions">
          <div class="yousay">
            Are there limits on who you can accomodate right now?
          </div>
          <div class="">
            <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="veteransOnly" /><label
              class="btn btn-outline-primary"
              for="veteransOnly"
              >Veterans only</label
            >
            <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="patientsOnly" /><label
              class="btn btn-outline-primary"
              for="patientsOnly"
              >Current patients only</label
            >
            <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="countyOnly" /><label
              class="btn btn-outline-primary"
              for="countyOnly"
              >County residents only</label
            >
          </div>
          <div class="instructions small secondary">
            If they say anything that's not on the list, mention it in the
            public notes.
          </div>

          <div class="yousay">
            Can you confirm that your address is {{ locationAddress }}
          </div>
          <div class="instructions">
            If that's wrong,
            <a
              target="_blank"
              class="text-muted small"
              href="https://airtable.com/shrY44NvEjHBscrOH?prefill_Location={{locationId}}&prefill_Type=Incorrect+contact+information"
              >Report an error</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>

    <div class="yousay">Thanks so much for your time! Have a great day.</div>

    <div>
      <div>Public notes</div>
      <div
        id="callScriptPublicNotes"
        class="input form-control form-control-sm"
        role="textbox"
        contenteditable
      >
        {{ locationPublicNotes }}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div>Private notes</div>
      <div
        id="callScriptPrivateNotes"
        class="input border border-secondary form-control form-control-sm"
        role="textbox"
        contenteditable
      >{{ locationPrivateNotes }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-6 mx-auto row">
      <input
        type="button"
        class="btn btn-primary"
        id="scoobyRecordCall"
        value="Send report"
      />
  </div>
</form>
